OL,3,CAbduction of boy and approach to
OL,4,Cyoungster in park may be linked, say
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FA seven-year-old boy was approached
OL,8,Fand threatened by a man a day after a
OL,9,Ffour-year-old was abducted in two
OL,10,Fincidents police are potentially
OL,11,Flinking.
OL,13,FThe seven-year-old boy was playing at
OL,14,FStevens Park, off Thorns Road, Quarry
OL,15,FBank, in Dudley, at about 5.55pm on
OL,16,FFriday, when he was approached by
OL,17,Fsomeone thought to be in their late
OL,18,Fteens or early 20s, West Midlands
OL,19,FPolice said.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
