PN,34602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1782325132
OL,3,CAbduction of boy and approach to
OL,4,Cyoungster in park may be linked, say
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FThe boy was asked if he wanted to ride
OL,8,Fthe man's bike and, when the child
OL,9,Fsaid no, the man threatened him,
OL,10,Fpolice said.
OL,12,FThe boy was not physically harmed and
OL,13,Flater reported the incident.
OL,15,FOfficers carried out a search of the
OL,16,Farea and reviewed CCTV footage as part
OL,17,Fof an ongoing investigation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1782325132
OL,3,CAbduction of boy and approach to
OL,4,Cyoungster in park may be linked, say
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FPolice say the suspect is described as
OL,8,Fbeing mixed race with dark brown, afro
OL,9,Fstyle hair, police said. He was
OL,10,Fwearing a T-shirt and shorts and
OL,11,Friding a dark blue bike.
OL,13,FIt follows an incident where a four-
OL,14,Fyear-old boy was abducted at Haden
OL,15,FHill Park in Cradley Heath, about four
OL,16,Fmiles away, the day before, says
OL,17,Fofficers.
OL,19,FThe incident took place shortly before
OL,20,F3.45pm at the park off Halesowen Road.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1782325132
OL,3,CAbduction of boy and approach to
OL,4,Cyoungster in park may be linked, say
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FThe boy, who was playing near the fish
OL,8,Fpond, went missing for a short period
OL,9,Fand was found in woodland close by,
OL,10,Fpolice said.
OL,12,FOfficers said the suspect was
OL,13,Fdescribed as being in his late teens,
OL,14,Fblack, short in height and with curled
OL,15,Fhair. He has been described as clean
OL,16,Fshaven and wearing black clothing.
OL,18,FThe force said officers are
OL,19,F"potentially linking the two incidents
OL,20,Fbut we are keeping an open mind".
OL,26,@{D@AOU|D@`O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
