CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1782325132
OL,3,CAbduction of boy and approach to
OL,4,Cyoungster in park may be linked, say
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FA spokesperson said: "We understand
OL,8,Fhow concerning incidents of this
OL,9,Fnature can be and we're working
OL,10,Ftirelessly on the investigation and to
OL,11,Festablish the exact circumstances.
OL,13,F"We're currently studying CCTV at both
OL,14,Flocations. We are also appealing for
OL,15,Fwitnesses to come forward and we're
OL,16,Fparticularly keen to hear from people
OL,17,Fwho may have been at the two park
OL,18,Flocations at the time and may have any
OL,19,Fmobile footage to please contact us."
OL,26,@oD@VOUuD@AOU{D@eO]
